      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The largest electrical concern in\nthe city had employed during the\nsummer month between 30 and 40\nmen on construction work. This\nforce has been reduced to a mere\nhandful. 1t was stated yesterday\nthat the big firm would, In the near\nfuture, declare for the open shop\"\non the grounds that the number of\nnonunion shops now doing busi-\nness in the city has made it prac-\ntically impossible for the union\nshop to secure contracts, as it Is\nunderbid in nearly every instance."
